- This solution is more suitable for a small dog because it provides a soft, breathable, and washable material that can be easily cleaned.
- The pillowcase can be used as a base, and the old socks can be stuffed inside to provide additional cushioning and warmth.
- This solution is also more hygienic than the plastic bag solution, as it can be easily washed and dried.

